name: Chibeast #3/25
description:
Chibeast is a collection of monsters chibi based on fantasy dungeon creature in RPG. And every piece is manually crafted pixel art. This collection has dungeon-dwelling monsters such as Orcs, Goblins, Skeletons and some Minotaurs.

This collection is Suitable for TCG (Trading Card Game) or for your D&D Session.
